# ===================================================
# SeaBattle_1_test.dat - Comprehensive Test Data
# ===================================================
# Format: TEST_TYPE param1 param2 ...
#
# TEST_TYPES:
#   BOARD_INIT size
#   SHIP_PLACE size x y orient len symbol
#   SHOT x y expected_result
#
# Parameters:
#   size - board size (10-26)
#   x, y - coordinates (0-based)
#   orient - orientation (0=horizontal left, 1=vertical up)
#   len - ship length (1-4)
#   symbol - ship symbol (A-Z)
#   expected_result - 0=miss, 1=hit, 2=sunk
#
# Notes:
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - Empty lines are ignored
#   - SHOT tests are sequential (use same board)
#   - Each SHOT sequence shares the same board state
# ===================================================

